title: 281.277 NOT TO AFFECT OTHER RIGHTS; DURATION.
text:
Nothing contained in sections 281.273 to 281.277 shall be construed to prejudice or preclude any right secured to any person under the Servicemembers Civil Relief Act, as amended.
Sections 281.273 to 281.277 shall remain in force as long as the Servicemembers Civil Relief Act, as amended, shall remain in force.
